fieldDocs.name: mode
fieldDocs.description: Returns the fixed mode for this field. How this mode is applied depends on the #modePolicy.

name: ModePolicy
description: Enumerates all policies of how to combine rule-based mode values with the effective field modes before rule application.

fieldDocs.name: OVERRIDE
fieldDocs.description: Override if effective mode is be NORMAL

fieldDocs.name: configureColumns
fieldDocs.description: Example for Datagrid column configuration. Stores columns in public.grid_columns

fieldDocs.name: iQuery
fieldDocs.description: Queries [T] objects based on the given query config

name: ValidationRules
description: Encapsulates the set of all named validation rules. Corresponds to the top-level rules.json file.
